S.FORM: a tja kineljang aicu a ti medea i tua milimilingan nua segeris (Greece) mavan aljak a vavayan nua mazangilj nua secolchis i aites (Aeëtes), a vuvu a vavayan nua cemas nua qadav i hilius . a kemasi sinansenay a tjiuguni ni hisiud (Hesiod) a tjevuta ti medea a kiseljang tjai djasun kati argunauc (Argonauts) namatazua i pasusangas tua 2700 a cavilj (700 BCE) a vinecikan tua milimilingan. == kasizuanan ==

a tja kineljang aico a ti medea i toa milimilingan noa segeris (Greece) mavan aljak a vavayan noa mazangilj noa secolchis i aites (Aeëtes), a vovo a vavayan noa cemas noa qadav i hilios . a kemasi sinansenay a tjiogoni ni hisiod (Hesiod) a tjevota ti medea a kiseljang tjai djason kati argonaoc (Argonaots) namatazoa i pasosangas toa 2700 a cavilj (700 BCE) a vinecikan toa milimilingan. == kasizoanan ==
